35  public function parse($modelClass) {
36  $instance = new $modelClass ();
37  $this->primaryKeys = Reflexion::getKeyFields ( $instance );
38  $this->oneToManyMembers = Reflexion::getMembersAnnotationWithAnnotation ( $modelClass, "@oneToMany" );

42  $this->joinTableMembers = Reflexion::getMembersAnnotationWithAnnotation ( $modelClass, "@joinTable" );
43  $this->transformers = Reflexion::getMembersAnnotationWithAnnotation ( $modelClass, "@transformer" );
44  $yuml = Reflexion::getAnnotationClass ( $modelClass, "@yuml" );
45  if (\sizeof ( $yuml ) > 0)
46  $this->yuml = $yuml [0];
47  $properties = Reflexion::getProperties ( $instance );
48  foreach ( $properties as $property ) {
49  $propName = $property->getName ();
50  $fieldName = Reflexion::getFieldName ( $modelClass, $propName );
51  $this->fieldNames [$propName] = $fieldName;
52  $nullable = Reflexion::isNullable ( $modelClass, $propName );
53  $serializable = Reflexion::isSerializable ( $modelClass, $propName );
54  if ($nullable)
55  $this->nullableMembers [] = $propName;
56  if (! $serializable)
57  $this->notSerializableMembers [] = $propName;
58  $type = Reflexion::getDbType ( $modelClass, $propName );
59  if ($type === false)
60  $type = "mixed";
61  $this->fieldTypes [$propName] = $type;
62  $accesseur = "set" . ucfirst ( $propName );
63  if (! isset ( $this->accessors [$fieldName] ) && method_exists ( $modelClass, $accesseur )) {
64  $this->accessors [$fieldName] = $accesseur;
65  }
66  }
67 
68  $this->global ["#tableName"] = Reflexion::getTableName ( $modelClass );
69  }

121  }
